name: Otsego ball chair
description: The Otsego ball chair is our reproduction of a classic, 1960s icon and is made of a white fiberglass shell with swivel pedestal base. It is truly difficult to describe what it is like to sit inside this piece -- you are completely enveloped in your own spherical cocoon. With its fully upholstered interior, this chair is incredibly comfortable and a wonderful space in which to curl up and take a quick nap. The exterior muffles approximately 75% of the noise and visual stimuli in your environment allowing you to simply relax or enjoy a focused conversation with a companion sitting across from you. name: Otselic bubble chair
description: Our Otselic bubble chair is a reproduction of a classic mid-century modern design. It is made from high density acrylic, outfitted with two foam cushions that are upholstered in leatherette or fabric, and is suitable for indoor or outdoor use. Suspended by a 6ft stainless steel chain on hooks, it makes quite the impression in any space. The unique round interior is an excellent way to listen to music as it encompasses the sitter in a way that shield them from surrounding noise, creating a dome-like effect. People enjoy the feeling of being suspended in air when sitting in this chair. This chair has been featured in numerous films and its iconic place in history is well-known.

name: Geneva fabric sectional sofa
description: Our Geneva furniture collection is designed after the classic mid-century designer pieces. This Geneva sectional sofa is available with a left or right facing chaise and features an exposed metal frame and legs of heavy gauge square, tubular steel in a polished chrome finish - the steel used is generally twice as thick as other reproductions. Constructed from a solid wood inner frame with a slightly pitched seat back angle, it is upholstered in our selection of quality custom fabrics and features fully welted and button tuft detailing on the seat and back cushions. The variable density foam cushions are "Velcro-ed" into place for easy removal and cleaning, over a no-sag suspension seat base. If you have a specific requirement for a project, we’re happy to help. name: Ann egg chair footstool - leather
description: Our reproduction leather egg chair footstool honors the original design from the late 1950s and celebrated for over 40 years. The Ann egg chair footstool features a base of satin-chromed aluminum or steel, with a swivel mechanism and adjustable height. Its molded fiberglass frame is finished with a genuine leather or hide (with unique natural hide pattern variations) over fire-retardant polyurethane foam padding, and is also separately available in a selection of fine wool and other fabrics. The upholstery is hand stitched to the shell with the same attention to detail found on the Egg Chair. The Footstool is especially useful for the user who likes to lean back and take advantage of the Egg Chair's tilting mechanism. If you have a specific requirement for a project, we’re happy to help. name: Denning coffee table
description: This round Depeyster coffee table is our reproduction of the mid-century classic dimple plywood design. Using the same technology that led to the invention of the iconic molded plywood lounge chairs, the original designers designed their Plywood Coffee Table (1946) to have a lean, shapely form that was durable yet lightweight. Its "saucer"-like top and curved legs makes a versatile coffee table for both traditional and modern space and is available in clear-coat Light Ash or Walnut, or stained Natural Cherry or Ebony veneer.

name: Greenport dining chair
description: The Greenport dining chair is our reproduction J39 dining chair by Borge Mogensen. The J39 is Borge Mogensen's most successful chair, inspired by his teacher Kaare Klint and American Shaker furniture. He designed the simple woven chair while development head of the furniture department of FDB, the Danish co-operative chain. The department's ambition was to make beautiful high-quality furniture available to everyone. They were particularly successful with the J39, now a classic piece of furniture for settings ranging from canteens and conference rooms to churches and private homes.

name: Sandlake oval tulip table base only
description: Popular options for the modern home's living and dining rooms, our versatile Sandlake collection includes quality reproductions of the classic mid-century tulip table design. If you have specific needs for your own custom Saarinen-style oval tulip table, and only require the base, here is your solution. This oval tulip dining table base is true to the original proportions, made of a heavy duty aluminum molded construction coated in a scratch and scuff resistant black or white high gloss finish. Crafted with four pre-drilled holes so you can attach it to almost any type of custom material or custom size top, this tulip table base is not recommended for oval marble tops larger than 78 inches long. Our replica tulip dining, coffee, side, and bar tables are available in a wide selection of custom sizes, configurations, and materials. name: scout sectional
description: This smartly tailored, architecturally shaped sectional looks truly polished atop its stainless steel base. Button-tufted seat and back cushions take it in a dressy, uptown direction, and the bench style seats make it great for a casual afternoon of just lounging around. Comfortable, contemporary and classy - that just about says it all. As with the entire Younger Furniture Collection, the scout sofa is completely American Made using the finest materials and most talented craftsmen available. The end result an extra-luxurious feel and sleek modern design that you can enjoy for many years to come. All Younger Furniture comes with our Limited Lifetime Warranty, 10-year spring and cushion warranty. It is constructed with heavy, 8-gauge, sinuous no-sag springs - closely spaced, secured with a webbing strap and a double row of tie wire - to create a comfortable, supportive and durable seat. The legs are made of resilient hardwood or stainless steel, with bases in different shapes and sizes to enhance each style.The long-life seat cushions are made of High Resiliency (HR) 2.0 minimum density foam, wrapped in multiple layers of polyester fiber and encased in a non-woven ticking material. We also offer a Feather-and-Down cushion upgrade. All Younger Collection items are double padded using propex and a layer of foam to reinforce the fabric to create a double layer of both strength and comfort.

description: A highly detailed reproduction of the original mid-century design, our Geneseo credenza sideboard is a versatile storage unit that is equally at ease in a modern home or executive office setting.
